  ],
  "remarks": "Chinaoil (Hong Kong) Corporation Limited is a Chinese company based in Hong Kong. It is a significant buyer of crude oil products of Russian origin. The energy sector, in particular the oil sector, is a sector providing substantial revenue to the Russian Government. Therefore, Chinaoil (Hong Kong) Corporation Limited is involved in an economic sector providing a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation.",
